Definition: the right of married persons to the enjoyment of association and sympathy and confidence and domestic happiness and the comfort of living together and eating meals at the same table and profiting from joint property right and the intimacies of domestic relations
Synonyms: legal_right, the, right, of, married, persons, to, enjoyment, association, and, sympathy, confidence, domestic, happiness, comfort, living, together, eating, meals, at, same, table, profiting, from, joint, property, intimacies, relations
Category: noun.attribute
